title.rendered: VIDEO: Prestige Motorcars X GAS Car Club Morning Run

content.rendered:
Usually as a stress reliever and to get together with friends, car people would arrange these cruises around the Jakarta highways. We at Prestige Motorcars held one of these morning cruises with our fellow car club friends, GAS Car Club. Lots of exciting cars and good vibes. Until the next run!
